@title kyberProxy for kyberNetwork contract
  The contract provides the following functions:
  - Get rates
  - Trade execution
  - Simple T2E, E2T and T2T trade APIs
  - Has some checks in place to safeguard takers

getExpectedRate(address,address,uint256).details: Get expected rate for a trade from src to dest tokens, with amount srcQty (no platform fee)

params.srcQty: Amount of src tokens in twei

returns.expectedRate: for a trade after deducting network fee. Rate = destQty (twei) / srcQty (twei) * 10 ** 18
returns.worstRate: for a trade. Usually expectedRate * 97 / 100             Use worstRate value as trade min conversion rate at your own risk

getExpectedRateAfterFee(address,address,.details: Get expected rate for a trade from src to dest tokens, amount srcQty and fees

params.hint: Advanced instructions for running the trade
params.platformFeeBps: Part of the trade that is allocated as fee to platform wallet. Ex: 10000 = 100%, 100 = 1%
params.srcQty: Amount of src tokens in twei

returns.expectedRate: for a trade after deducting network + platform fee             Rate = destQty (twei) / srcQty (twei) * 10 ** 18

swapEtherToToken(address,uint256).details: Trade from eth -> token. Sends token to msg sender

params.minConversionRate: The minimal conversion rate. If actual rate is lower, trade reverts

returns._0: Amount of actual dest tokens in twei

swapTokenToEther(address,uint256,uint256.details: Trade from token -> eth. Sends eth to msg sender

params.minConversionRate: The minimal conversion rate. If actual rate is lower, trade reverts
params.srcAmount: Amount of src tokens in twei

returns._0: Amount of actual dest tokens in twei

swapTokenToToken(address,uint256,address.details: Trade from src to dest token. Sends dest tokens to msg sender

params.minConversionRate: The minimal conversion rate. If actual rate is lower, trade reverts
params.srcAmount: Amount of src tokens in twei

returns._0: Amount of actual dest tokens in twei

trade(address,uint256,address,address,ui.details: Trade from src to dest token and sends dest token to destAddress

params.maxDestAmount: A limit on the amount of dest tokens in twei
params.minConversionRate: The minimal conversion rate. If actual rate is lower, trade reverts
params.platformWallet: Platform wallet address for receiving fees
params.srcAmount: Amount of src tokens in twei

returns._0: Amount of actual dest tokens in twei

params.maxDestAmount: A limit on the amount of dest tokens in twei
params.minConversionRate: The minimal conversion rate. If actual rate is lower, trade reverts
